      "text": "I'm gonna say it every time that my mind is all right",
      "start": 28.479999542236328
    },
    {
      "end": 36.81999969482422,
      "text": "Girl, I'm never gonna be the one there for you",
      "start": 32.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 40.86000061035156,
      "text": "Now hey, I'm never gonna be the one there for you",
      "start": 36.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 43.84000015258789,
      "text": "Now that you know it and I hear you",
      "start": 40.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 47.36000061035156,
      "text": "Now that you know, know, know me",
      "start": 44.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 49.34000015258789,
      "text": "Now find another one",
      "start": 47.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 53.040000915527344,
      "text": "I'm never gonna be the one there for you",
      "start": 49.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 57.099998474121094,
      "text": "Oh, girl, I'm never gonna be the one there for you",
      "start": 53.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 61.08000183105469,
      "text": "No, I never did it in the manual of the night",
